{"data":[{"date":"07:11 20/07","title":"Fabinho: \u201cT\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u1ed1 r\u1ee7 r\u00ea Mbappe t\u1edbi Liverpool\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/fabinho-toi-dang-co-ru-re-mbappe-toi-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Monaco, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Fabinho thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Mbappe t\u1edbi Liverpool \u2013 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nFabinho c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o Mbappe<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u0103m nay, Fabinho l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Kylian Mbappe ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u00e2y s\u1ed1t tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, ghi 4 b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 gi\u00fap \u0110T Ph\u00e1p gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi. Anh cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Khi t\u00f4i t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Kylian \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi m\u1ed9t tin nh\u1eafn ch\u00fac m\u1eebng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ch\u00fac m\u1eebng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u00ec tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0m c\u00f9ng \u0110T th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, Kylian l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, m\u1ed9t t\u00e0i n\u0103ng l\u1edbn.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp theo s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i PSG. Kh\u00f4ng sao c\u1ea3, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1eadu \u1ea5y gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool. T\u00f4i c\u00f9ng r\u1ea5t th\u00e2n v\u1edbi Bernardo Silva c\u00f9ng Benjamin Mendy. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng t\u1edbi Anh thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Ngo\u00e0i s\u00e2n c\u1ecf, t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u00f2 chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi h\u1ecd, nh\u01b0ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00e1c.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Fabinho thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Mbappe t\u1edbi Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Fabinho thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Mbappe t\u1edbi Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/Fabinho-thuyet-phuc-Mbappe-toi-Liverpool-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Fabinho thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Mbappe sang Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nFabinho chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh: &ldquo;Khi t\u1edbi Real Madrid, t\u00f4i m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 18, 19 tu\u1ed5i. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 n\u0103m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, khi \u0111\u00f3 t\u00f4i c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t tr\u1ebb. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng si\u00eau sao l\u00fac \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Cris Ronaldo, Mesut Ozil, Luka Modric. Kinh nghi\u1ec7m ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng cho Real Madrid B gi\u00fap t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, v\u00e0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf Liverpool &ndash; m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/\" title=\" bong da\" type=\" bong da\">b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span> h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. Liverpool c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t HLV xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc. T\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u Man City \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, nh\u01b0ng Liverpool s\u1ebd l\u00e0m h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed5 ngai v\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd, khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c C\u0110V c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac&rdquo; &ndash; Fabinho k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, The Kop \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh khi \u0111em v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 Alisson Becker. Bi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e2u \u0111\u1ea5y, trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Fabinho thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Mbappe t\u1edbi Liverpool s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/voi-alisson-premier-league-chiem-tron-hang-thu-dat-gia-nhat-hanh-tinh-172-191635.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/26/voi-alisson-premier-league-chiem-tron-hang-thu-dat-gia-nhat-hanh-tinh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/voi-alisson-premier-league-chiem-tron-hang-thu-dat-gia-nhat-hanh-tinh-172-191635.html\">V\u1edbi Alisson, Premier League chi\u1ebfm tr\u1ecdn h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson Becker v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb h\u01a1n...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-chia-se-nguyen-nhan-bien-alisson-thanh-thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi-172-191634.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/klopp-chia-se-nguyen-nhan-bien-alisson-thanh-thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi.jpeg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-chia-se-nguyen-nhan-bien-alisson-thanh-thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi-172-191634.html\">Klopp chia s\u1ebb nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n bi\u1ebfn Alisson th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</span><br>\r\nSau nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i, r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. HLV Jurgen Klopp chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Alisson v\u00e0 t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u1eadu...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1438","checkdouble":"191637"},{"date":"07:34 20/07","title":"Ibra ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi M.U","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/ibra-tiet-lo-nguyen-nhan-buoc-phai-roi-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau khi y\u00ean \u1ed5n t\u1ea1i MLS, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Zlatan Ibrahimovic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 M.U c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nIbra bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean ghi b\u00e0n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u CLB trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean &ndash; 27 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 45 tr\u1eadn, Ibra \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a Rooney v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c M.U gia h\u1ea1n th\u00eam 1 n\u0103m. Nh\u01b0ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ee9 2, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 ghi v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u00e2y ch\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i Old Trafford, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 36 tu\u1ed5i cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;M\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n x\u1ecf gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o s\u00e2n, t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng cho ph\u00e9p t\u00f4i thi \u0111\u1ea5u. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn l\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00e0ng tu\u1ea7n, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n nong, h\u00e3y gi\u1eef l\u1ea5y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u00e0 t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Nh\u01b0ng tinh th\u1ea7n d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng, \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u1ea1i n\u00f3i \u0111i\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, M.U \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu Zlatan. C\u00f2n t\u00f4i v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3 ch\u01b0a s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0 Zlatan. T\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn trong nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eb3ng th\u1eebng v\u1edbi Mourinho: &lsquo;Nghe n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, h\u00e3y ch\u1ecdn ai \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n&rsquo;.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ibrahimovic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU va nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ibrahimovic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU va nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/ibra.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ibrahimovic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, Ibra c\u0169ng d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169: &ldquo;Paul Pogba \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 b\u1eb1ng l\u1eddi. Nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3. Pogba c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t tr\u1ebb, \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u cao qu\u00fd.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Rooney, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/\" title=\"bong da\" type=\"bong da\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span></span> theo m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c t\u1ea1i MLS. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn. Gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u00e0 ngh\u1ec1 M\u1ef9 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi Rooney, gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 n\u00f3 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i. Rooney n\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh, l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1eadu \u1ea5y gi\u1ecfi nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y&rdquo; &ndash; Ibrahimovic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 M.U v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/ibrahimovic-bi-troll-boi-rooney-va-beckham-sau-tran-thua-cua-thuy-dien-465-190650.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/ibrahimovic-bi-troll-boi-rooney-va-beckham-sau-tran-thua-cua-thuy-dien.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/ibrahimovic-bi-troll-boi-rooney-va-beckham-sau-tran-thua-cua-thuy-dien-465-190650.html\">Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn, Ibrahimovic b\u1ecb troll v\u00ec l\u1ee1 d\u1ea1i \u0111\u1eb7t c\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi Beckham</span><br>\r\nSau khi \u0110T Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, Zlatan Ibrahimovic b\u1ecb troll b\u1edfi Rooney c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh sau m\u00e0n \u0111\u00e1nh c\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00fa v\u1ecb v\u1edbi David Beckham.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/ibrahimovic-khen-pogba-sau-danh-hieu-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-469-191326.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/ibrahimovic-khen-pogba-sau-danh-hieu-vo-dich-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/ibrahimovic-khen-pogba-sau-danh-hieu-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-469-191326.html\">Ibrahimovic khen Pogba sau danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nZlatan Ibrahimovic \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi khen c\u00f3 c\u00e1nh cho Pogba sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi Croatia \u0111\u00eam qua.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1437","checkdouble":"191638"},{"date":"07:48 20/07","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! Nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o c\u1ee7a Alisson v\u1edbi Karius","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/day-nhung-con-so-cho-thay-su-ap-dao-cua-alisson-voi-karius.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 bom t\u1ea5n 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y trang th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Opta \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 so s\u00e1nh Alisson v\u1edbi Karius.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nAlisson \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda Karius<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Liverpool v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi k\u00edch n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Alisson Becker. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng xem th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil c\u00f3 g\u00ec h\u01a1n Loris Karius qua nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>28 &ndash;</strong> Alisson l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi 28 b\u00e0n thua trong 37 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i Serie A m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, \u00edt h\u01a1n 10 b\u00e0n so v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Mignolet (24) v\u00e0 Karius (14) t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>109 &ndash;</strong> Alisson c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 109 pha c\u1ee9u thua \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, g\u1ea7n g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 Mignolet (36) v\u00e0 Karius (31).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>79,3 &ndash; </strong>T\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Alisson Becker. Nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Mignolet/Karius l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00e0 59,3 v\u00e0 68,9%.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 so s\u00e1nh Alisson v\u1edbi Karius h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 so s\u00e1nh Alisson v\u1edbi Karius h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/karius.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 so s\u00e1nh Alisson v\u1edbi Karius</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><br>\r\n0 &ndash;</strong> Alisson kh\u00f4ng m\u1eafc b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 sai l\u1ea7m n\u00e0o d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua, trong khi Mignolet c\u00f3 3 v\u00e0 Karius c\u00f3 2.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>118,9 &ndash;</strong> Kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian trung b\u00ecnh Alisson l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi, kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi Karius (122 ph\u00fat/b\u00e0n thua). Tuy nhi\u00ean, Karius b\u1eaft \u00edt h\u01a1n Alisson t\u1edbi 18 tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>47 &ndash;</strong> S\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Alisson m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, trong khi Mignolet v\u00e0 Karius nh\u1eadn t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 61 b\u00e0n thua sau 55 tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>8,31 </strong>&ndash; S\u1ed1 trung b\u00ecnh Alisson t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i &lsquo;b\u00e0n th\u1eafng k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng&rsquo; (n\u00f3i \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 anh c\u1ee9u thua trung b\u00ecnh 8,31 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nguy hi\u1ec3m khi \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t), ch\u1ec9 sau Nick Pope (10,26) v\u00e0 David De Gea (13,66) tr\u00ean kh\u1eafp ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. \u0110\u1ec3 so s\u00e1nh, con s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Karius l\u00e0 -0,64, c\u00f2n Mignolet l\u00e0 -0,81 (ngh\u0129a l\u00e0&hellip; th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/voi-alisson-premier-league-chiem-tron-hang-thu-dat-gia-nhat-hanh-tinh-172-191635.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/26/voi-alisson-premier-league-chiem-tron-hang-thu-dat-gia-nhat-hanh-tinh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/voi-alisson-premier-league-chiem-tron-hang-thu-dat-gia-nhat-hanh-tinh-172-191635.html\">V\u1edbi Alisson, Premier League chi\u1ebfm tr\u1ecdn h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson Becker v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb h\u01a1n...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-chia-se-nguyen-nhan-bien-alisson-thanh-thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi-172-191634.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/klopp-chia-se-nguyen-nhan-bien-alisson-thanh-thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi.jpeg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-chia-se-nguyen-nhan-bien-alisson-thanh-thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi-172-191634.html\">Klopp chia s\u1ebb nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n bi\u1ebfn Alisson th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</span><br>\r\nSau nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i, r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. HLV Jurgen Klopp chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Alisson v\u00e0 t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u1eadu...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-liverpool-kich-no-bom-tan-alisson-172-191632.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/chinh-thuc-liverpool-kich-no-bom-tan-alisson.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-liverpool-kich-no-bom-tan-alisson-172-191632.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Liverpool k\u00edch n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n Alisson</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Alisson gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1436","checkdouble":"191639"},{"date":"08:05 20/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 20/7: Real Madrid ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1eb7t gi\u00e1 Hazard","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-207-real-madrid-chinh-thuc-dat-gia-hazard.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 20/7.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nReal Madrid ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1eb7t gi\u00e1 Hazard<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed T\u00e2y Ban Nha, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Real s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 Chelsea v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 B\u1ea3y tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb cho Hazard. M\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 ban \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00e0 Los Blancos chi tr\u1ea3 l\u00e0 125 tri\u1ec7u euro, v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u1edbn The Blues s\u1ebd t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, CLB Ho\u00e0ng gia c\u0169ng ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n Thibaut Courtois sau khi ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1ea3 35 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 20/7\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 207 Real Madrid ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1eb7t gi\u00e1 Hazard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/18/Diem-tin-bong-da-sang-207-Real-Madrid-chinh-thuc-dat-gia-Hazard-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 20/7: Real mu\u1ed1n mua b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Eden Hazard</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>Man City l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u1ed1ng c\u1ed5 Sterling<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Anh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 2 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Man City. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu anh kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn gia h\u1ea1n, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad s\u1ebd chia tay Sterling trong v\u00f2ng 12 th\u00e1ng t\u1edbi.&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>&ldquo;Gi\u00e1o s\u01b0&rdquo; nh\u1eadn l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb Nh\u1eadt<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, L\u0110B\u0110 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 m\u1eddi HLV Arsene Wenger d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia. T\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi m\u1ecdc ch\u1ec9 d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0110T B\u1ec9, nh\u01b0ng g\u00e2y ti\u1ebfng vang l\u1edbn khi d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi 2 b\u00e0n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao Juve<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, trung v\u1ec7 <span href=\"http://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-sap-cong-bo-tan-binh-thu-2-tri-gia-36-trieu-bang-172-191548.html\" target=\"_blank\">Daniele Rugani s\u1ebd gia nh\u1eadp The Blues</span> trong th\u1eddi gian s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t, sau khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 44,2 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng (bao g\u1ed3m ph\u1ee5 ph\u00ed) c\u00f9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 77 ngh\u00ecn b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n. \u0110\u1ec3 th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7, B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0 th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn s\u00e1t Diego Godin &ndash; trung v\u1ec7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00f3n tin vui tr\u00ean TTCN<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/day-dau-hieu-cho-thay-leicester-sap-co-danny-ward-172-191617.html\" target=\"_blank\">Leicester \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd chi ra 12,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Danny Ward</span> &ndash; \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i cho th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Kasper Schmeichel, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea theo s\u00e1t \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Courtois.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c s\u1edf h\u1eefu th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-liverpool-kich-no-bom-tan-alisson-172-191632.html\" target=\"_blank\">The Kop \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Alisson Becker t\u1eeb AS Roma</span>, sau khi ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi tr\u1ea3 56 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u00f9ng 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ph\u1ee5 ph\u00ed, khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 207 Real Madrid ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1eb7t gi\u00e1 Hazard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 207 Real Madrid ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1eb7t gi\u00e1 Hazard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/Diem-tin-bong-da-sang-207-Real-Madrid-chinh-thuc-dat-gia-Hazard-hinh-anh-2.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/\" title=\"bong da\" type=\"bong da\">b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span> s\u00e1ng 20/7: Alisson gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>M.U nh\u1eadn tin vui t\u1eeb Sanchez</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00f4i sao tr\u1ed1n thu\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd c\u1ee7a M\u1ef9, cho ph\u00e9p anh t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 tour du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Mourinho lo ng\u1ea1i Alexis Sanchez kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00ec r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i visa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1435","checkdouble":"191640"},{"date":"08:54 20/07","title":"\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Ph\u00e1p ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/20/doi-truong-phap-tiet-lo-dieu-dac-biet-sau-chien-thang-truoc-argentina.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Hugo Lloris ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p, \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Les Bleus ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 r\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Argentina \u0111\u1ea7y k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng C, Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p Argentina \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018, trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Argentina \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mong ch\u1edd nh\u1ea5t. NHM \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hugo Lloris ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Hugo Lloris ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/doi-truong-phap-tiet-lo-dieu-dac-biet-sau-chien-thang-truoc-argentina.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110T Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Argentina 4-3 \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 7 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 Argentina, c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u0103ng hoa. V\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, Les Bleus \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-3.\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Argentina ng\u1eadm ng\u00f9i r\u1eddi cu\u1ed9c ch\u01a1i. V\u1edbi th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina, Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t chu\u1ed7i 4 tr\u1eadn to\u00e0n thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Nam M\u1ef9. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng cho th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u cho danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Lloris \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hugo Lloris ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p, \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Les Bleus ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 r\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thu thanh Hugo Lloris tranh thu khoe huy chuong cua nha vo dich.\" title=\"Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Hugo Lloris tranh th\u1ee7 khoe huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/4E4F3BC500000578-5958631-image-a-142_1531743694542.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Hugo Lloris tin r\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Argentina c\u1ee7a Messi \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8, chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u00f3 mang l\u1ea1i ni\u1ec1m tin r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn cho to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. N\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i nh\u1eadn ra r\u1eb1ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cNh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n nh\u1ea5t\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPh\u00e1p c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u1edf World Cup 2018, theo \u0111\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mbappe \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t. Lloris v\u1edbi sai l\u1ea7m trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Croatia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t danh hi\u1ec7u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0o tay Courtois c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1434","checkdouble":"191641"},{"date":"20:38 19/07","title":"Nh\u0103m nhe sao tr\u1ebb, Barca nh\u1eadn c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o g\u1eaft t\u1eeb Ajax","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/ajax-gui-canh-bao-danh-thep-toi-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Barcelona \u0111ang \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft t\u1edbi c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Frenkie de Jong v\u00e0 Matthijs de Ligt c\u1ee7a Ajax. Nh\u01b0ng gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao, Marc Overmars ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Ajax l\u1ea1i t\u1ecf ra \u0111\u1ea7y c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Barca nh\u1eafm c\u00e1c sao tr\u1ebb Ajax</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00f2 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o Ajax c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 Lan lu\u00f4n thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o h\u00e0ng uy t\u00edn nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. H\u00e0ng n\u0103m, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u00e0u truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y cho ra m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb tri\u1ec3n v\u1ecdng song \u0111i k\u00e8m v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Frenkie de Jong v\u00e0 Matthijs de Ligt \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm. Trong \u0111\u00f3, Barcelona \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1t s\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t khi d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 c\u1ea3 c\u1eb7p t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Ajax.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Overmars ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Ajax \u0111\u1ea7y c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Overmars ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Ajax \u0111\u1ea7y c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/tien-ve-Frenkie-de-Jong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">De Jong n\u1eb1m trong t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm Barca</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nDe Jong (21 tu\u1ed5i) l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Barca. T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1, De Ligt m\u1edbi 18 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Ajax v\u00e0 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 7 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0110T H\u00e0 Lan.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ajax t\u1ecf ra c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao, Marc Overmars ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Ajax. \u00d4ng nh\u1eafn Barca r\u1eb1ng t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t n\u01a1i kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau binh. \u201cDe Jong kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e1n, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c b\u00ean li\u00ean quan\u201d, Overmars n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u1edd De Telegraaf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u0103m nhe sao tr\u1ebb, Barca nh\u1eadn c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o g\u1eaft t\u1eeb Ajax h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Nh\u0103m nhe sao tr\u1ebb, Barca nh\u1eadn c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o g\u1eaft t\u1eeb Ajax h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/Nham-nhe-sao-tre,-Barca-nhan-canh-bao-gat-tu-Ajax-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Overmars ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Ajax kh\u00e1 c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 l\u00e0 De Ligt. C\u00e1c CLB quan t\u00e2m s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ef1 do tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u00e0o n\u0103m t\u1edbi. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Davinson Sanchez (t\u1edbi Tottenham) n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i cho th\u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. H\u1ecd v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 19, 20 tu\u1ed5i. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n \u0111i\u00ean r\u1ed3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eedi t\u1edbi.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/tan-binh-barca-cap-ben-nou-camp-nho-neymar-180-191543.html\">T\u00e2n binh Barca c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Nou Camp nh\u1edd Neymar</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-quyet-dau-voi-real-vi-eden-hazard-180-191467.html\">Barca quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Real v\u00ec Eden Hazard</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/andre-gomes-muon-toi-tottenham-172-191411.html\">Sao th\u1ea5t s\u1ee7ng c\u1ee7a Barca mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1 c\u00f9ng Harry Kane t\u1ea1i Premier League</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-muon-vuot-mat-arsenal-vu-tien-ve-nzonzi-180-191340.html\">Barca mu\u1ed1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Arsenal v\u1ee5 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chan-mu-pogba-co-dong-thai-san-sang-dau-quan-cho-barca-172-191187.html\">Ch\u00e1n M.U, Pogba c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Barca</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1433","checkdouble":"191626"},{"date":"03:42 20/07","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP MU vs Club America 09h00 ng\u00e0y 20/7 (Giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/mu-vs-club-america-tran-dau-giao-huu-he-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp MU vs Club America: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 k\u00e8m link xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018 Club America vs MU l\u00fac 09h00 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 20/7.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n tham d\u1ef1 chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00f9a h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a MU n\u0103m nay c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1i t\u00ean \"l\u1ea1\" \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 hai t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb t\u1edbi t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i U18 l\u00e0 James Garner v\u00e0 Mason Greenwood, c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u sinh n\u0103m 2001. B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i c\u00e1nh Tahith Chong v\u00e0 Anges Gomes c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd. Th\u1ed1ng l\u0129nh h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \"Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\" trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 Anthony Martial do Alexis Sanchez ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i do v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 visa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, Jose Mourinho s\u1ebd c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y an t\u00e2m h\u01a1n \u1edf ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 khi \u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t. S\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Young \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Luke Shaw kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p v\u1edbi tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a MU m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp MU vs Club America tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018 s\u00e1ng nay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp MU vs Club America tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018 s\u00e1ng nay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/Club-America-vs-Man-United.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">MU vs Club America</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a MU t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 l\u00e0 Club America, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 12 l\u1ea7n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Mexico. \"Thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng\" c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Mexico l\u00e0 Miguel Herrera, c\u1ef1u HLV c\u1ee7a Mexico t\u1ea1i World Cup 2014. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 \"n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n\" c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Mourinho. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00e0 m\u00f9a n\u0103m 2015 v\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n th\u1eafng khi \u0111\u00f3 thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 MU v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Schneiderlin. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ba n\u0103m tr\u00f4i qua v\u1edbi qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i khi\u1ebfn k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n mang t\u00ednh tham kh\u1ea3o. Ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd ch\u1edd t\u00e0i c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Mourinho trong ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nDanh s\u00e1ch 23 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 MU tham d\u1ef1 chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00f9a h\u00e8 t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9<br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 m\u00f4n: Sergio Romero, Joel Pereira, Lee Grant<br>\r\nH\u1eadu v\u1ec7: Antonio Valencia, Matteo Darmian, Diogo Dalot, Timothy Fosu-Mensah, RoShaun Williams, Chris Smalling, Eric Bailly, Axel Tuanzebe, Demetri Mitchell, Luke Shaw<br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7: James Garner, Ander Herrera, Andreas Pereira, Scott McTominay, Ethan Hamilton<br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o: Tahith Chong, Angel Gomes, Juan Mata, Anthony Martial, Mason Greenwood, Joshua Bohui.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1432","checkdouble":"191627"},{"date":"21:14 19/07","title":"S\u1ebfp \u0110T Ph\u00e1p b\u00f3c tr\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 tin v\u1ec1 Zidane","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/27/sep-dt-phap-boc-tran-su-that-kho-tin-ve-zidane.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Alisson gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t.</h2><h2><br>\r\nLiverpool chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Alisson<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Anfield \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c k\u00edch n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n Alisson Becker t\u1eeb AS Roma, theo m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi d\u00e0nh cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a anh l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn <strong>65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng &ndash; bao g\u1ed3m ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng 56 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, c\u00f9ng 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ph\u1ee5 ph\u00ed,</strong> v\u01b0\u1ee3t xa k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u0169 34,7 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Ederson.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 25 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Liverpool, sau khi ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t bu\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf t\u1ea1i Melwood ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay. Alisson Becker \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Loris Karius &ndash; th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda trong khung g\u1ed7 \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng\" title=\"Alisson gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/chinh-thuc-liverpool-kich-no-bom-tan-alisson.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h2>Alisson gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 c\u1ea3m ngh\u0129 khi \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00fat k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u01b0\u1edbc m\u01a1 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt, khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u00e1c l\u00ean m\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o n\u00e0y, v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, khi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a CLB, m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea1i gia \u0111\u00ecnh Liverpool. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i&rdquo; &ndash; Alisson Becker h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 \u0110T Brazil \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi 17/37 tr\u1eadn ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i Serie A, v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 cao th\u1ee9 3 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u &ndash; ch\u1ec9 sau Jan Oblak v\u00e0 David De Gea. Anh l\u00e0 m\u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool, khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 Fabinho, Keita v\u00e0 Shaqiri m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-blackburn-02-liverpool-giao-huu-he-2018-326-191631.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/tong-hop-blackburn-02-liverpool-giao-huu-he-2018.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-blackburn-02-liverpool-giao-huu-he-2018-326-191631.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Blackburn 0-2 Liverpool (Giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018)</span><br>\r\nHai pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng trong hi\u1ec7p 2 c\u1ee7a Markovic v\u00e0 Sturridge gi\u00fap L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c th\u1ebf l\u1ef1c m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Premier League nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd \u0111ang ch\u01a1i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t trong...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/mat-alisson-sep-roma-van-day-tu-tin-176-191624.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/mat-alisson-sep-roma-van-day-tu-tin.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/mat-alisson-sep-roma-van-day-tu-tin-176-191624.html\">M\u1ea5t Alisson, s\u1ebfp Roma v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin</span><br>\r\nMonchi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 AS Roma. Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7y tham v\u1ecdng d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t, m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Alisson sang...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1431","checkdouble":"191628"},{"date":"21:54 19/07","title":"T\u00e2n binh Chelsea: \u201cT\u00f4i l\u00e0 c\u1ee7a hi\u1ebfm c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/tan-binh-chelsea-toi-la-cua-hiem-cua-nuoc-anh.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jorginho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau khi gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1eefng k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a anh l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u t\u1ea1i Premier League.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Jorginho l\u00e0 c\u1ee7a hi\u1ebfm c\u1ee7a EPL</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Napoli, Jorginho n\u1ed5i l\u00ean nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m hay nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn Chelsea ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u00ean t\u1edbi 57 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 anh. Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Italia \u0111ang h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1eed s\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u00f3 l\u1ebd phong c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u t\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh\u201d, Jorginho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau khi gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea. \u201cT\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng s\u1ebd th\u00edch nghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y. T\u00f4i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u00e2n binh Chelsea T\u00f4i l\u00e0 c\u1ee7a hi\u1ebfm c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u00e2n binh Chelsea T\u00f4i l\u00e0 c\u1ee7a hi\u1ebfm c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/Untitled.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Chelsea c\u00f3 Jorginho v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 57 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i th\u00edch ch\u01a1i b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m, nh\u1eadn b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. T\u00f4i lu\u00f4n th\u00edch nh\u1eefng th\u1eed th\u00e1ch v\u00e0 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi s\u1ebd l\u00e0 th\u1eed th\u00e1ch l\u1edbn. Nh\u01b0ng n\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 truy\u1ec1n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng cho t\u00f4i. C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00edch l\u0169y kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 t\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>T\u1ef1 tin ch\u01a1i d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a Sarri</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u00e2n binh Chelsea T\u00f4i l\u00e0 c\u1ee7a hi\u1ebfm c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"T\u00e2n binh Chelsea T\u00f4i l\u00e0 c\u1ee7a hi\u1ebfm c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/Tan-binh-Chelsea-Toi-la-cua-hiem-cua-nuoc-Anh-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Jorginho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau khi gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea v\u00e0 v\u1ec1 HLV\u00a0Sarri</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh nh\u01b0ng Jorginho s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p HLV Maurizio Sarri, th\u1ea7y c\u0169 t\u1ea1i Napoli. Anh mong \u0111\u1ee3i s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd s\u1ebd mang l\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa. \u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi tri\u1ebft l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Sarri\u201d, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i n\u00f3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cKhi c\u00f2n \u1edf Napoli, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t \u0103n \u00fd. T\u00f4i gi\u00fap \u00f4ng \u1ea5y truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i \u00fd \u0111\u1ed3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt th\u00f4ng qua kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nJorginho n\u1eb1m trong danh s\u00e1ch 25 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean Chelsea t\u1edbi Australia du \u0111\u1ea5u trong v\u00f2ng 1 tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi. H\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i v\u1edbi Perth Glory v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 23 th\u00e1ng 7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Chelsea tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-chelsea-gian-nan-vi-thoi-duong-ho-di-hoa-172-191620.html\">G\u00f3c Chelsea: Gian nan v\u00ec th\u00f3i \u201cd\u01b0\u1ee1ng h\u1ed5 di h\u1ecda\u201d</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-dau-hieu-cho-thay-leicester-sap-co-danny-ward-172-191617.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! D\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u cho th\u1ea5y Chelsea s\u1eafp c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng World Cup</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/khong-the-gay-soc-vu-alisson-chelsea-chuyen-huong-sang-donnarumma-172-191596.html\">Chelsea chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 19 tu\u1ed5i thay Courtois</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-sarri-chi-ra-vi-tri-yeu-nhat-cua-chelsea-172-191580.html\">HLV Sarri ch\u1ec9 ra v\u1ecb tr\u00ed y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tan-hlv-chelsea-thua-nhan-khong-thich-tieu-tien-172-191577.html\">T\u00e2n HLV Chelsea th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch ti\u00eau ti\u1ec1n</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1430","checkdouble":"191629"},{"date":"22:29 19/07","title":"M.U \u0111\u00f3n tin c\u1ef1c vui v\u1ec1 Alexis Sanchez","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/22/mu-don-tin-cuc-vui-ve-alexis-sanchez.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Alexis Sanchez \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p sang M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i M.U. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 khi nh\u1eefng r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i v\u1ec1 visa \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Sanchez \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft xong visa</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ed1i 15/7 v\u1eeba qua, Man United \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00ean m\u00e1y bay sang M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ri\u00eang ng\u00f4i sao Alexis Sanchez c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 nh\u1eadp c\u1ea3nh v\u00e0o x\u1ee9 c\u1edd hoa. L\u00fd do l\u00e0 b\u1edfi anh \u0111ang th\u1ee5 \u00e1n t\u00f9 treo 16 th\u00e1ng v\u00ec b\u1ecb k\u1ebft t\u1ed9i tr\u1ed1n thu\u1ebf trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha cho Barcelona.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 sang M\u1ef9, Sanchez bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i quay l\u1ea1i trung t\u00e2m Carrington t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh. Trong th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00f3, CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n M.U \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft nh\u1eefng kh\u00fac m\u1eafc cho tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Chile.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sanchez \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p sang M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sanchez \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p sang M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/1/Sanchez-duoc-phep-sang-My-du-dau-cung-toan-doi-MU-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Sanchez \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p sang M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1eadt may l\u00e0 m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n sau c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft. Sanchez ch\u1ee9ng minh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1eb1ng minh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tu\u00e2n th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00fang ph\u00e1p lu\u1eadt trong th\u1eddi gian h\u01b0\u1edfng \u00e1n treo v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c M.U b\u1ea3o l\u00e3nh. Anh m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p visa sang M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi Club America (Mexico) v\u00e0o 9h s\u00e1ng mai (20/7).<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mourinho th\u1edf ph\u00e0o</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u00f4ng tin Sanchez \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p sang M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u khi\u1ebfn HLV Jose Mourinho c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y vui m\u1eebng. \u00d4ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y m\u1eb7t m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao m\u1edbi d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 tr\u00ean x\u1ee9 c\u1edd hoa. Nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tham d\u1ef1 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tr\u1edf \u0111i t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ph\u00e9p th\u00eam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho va Sanchez\" title=\"Mourinho va Sanchez\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/22/Sanchez-chia-se-ve-khoi-dau-kho-khan-o-MU-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mourinho nh\u1eadn tin vui t\u1eeb Sanchez</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nRi\u00eang c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Anh, Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 B\u1ec9 trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh M.U s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a. T\u00ednh ra, s\u1ebd c\u00f3 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Premier League do ch\u01b0a k\u1ecbp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau k\u1ef3 ngh\u0129. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00ec th\u1ebf, vi\u1ec7c Sanchez c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf M\u1ef9 c\u00e0ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft h\u01a1n. Mourinho mu\u1ed1n ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile t\u1eadp d\u01b0\u1ee3t c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c v\u1ec7 tinh xung quanh \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League v\u1edbi Leicester v\u00e0o r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 11/8 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Man United tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/lich-thi-dau-giao-huu-he-2018-cua-mu-172-191607.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/adnan-januzaj-sap-tro-lai-ngoai-hang-anh-doi-dau-mu-172-191599.html\">Adnan Januzaj s\u1eafp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-nhan-don-dau-vu-bonucci-172-191595.html\">MU nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00f2n \u0111au v\u1ee5 sao kh\u1ee7ng Italia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-co-vai-loi-muon-gui-den-paul-pogba-172-191552.html\">Mourinho c\u00f3 v\u00e0i l\u1eddi mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn Paul Pogba</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-muon-danh-ca-cum-bayern-munich-172-191550.html\">MU mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1nh c\u1ea3 c\u1ee5m Bayern Munich</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1429","checkdouble":"191630"},{"date":"05:45 20/07","title":"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Liverpool k\u00edch n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n Alisson","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/chinh-thuc-liverpool-kich-no-bom-tan-alisson.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Alisson gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t.</h2><h2><br>\r\nLiverpool chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Alisson<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Anfield \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c k\u00edch n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n Alisson Becker t\u1eeb AS Roma, theo m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi d\u00e0nh cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a anh l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn <strong>65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng &ndash; bao g\u1ed3m ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng 56 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, c\u00f9ng 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ph\u1ee5 ph\u00ed,</strong> v\u01b0\u1ee3t xa k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u0169 34,7 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Ederson.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 25 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Liverpool, sau khi ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t bu\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf t\u1ea1i Melwood ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay. Alisson Becker \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Loris Karius &ndash; th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda trong khung g\u1ed7 \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng\" title=\"Alisson gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/chinh-thuc-liverpool-kich-no-bom-tan-alisson.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h2>Alisson gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 c\u1ea3m ngh\u0129 khi \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00fat k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u01b0\u1edbc m\u01a1 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt, khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u00e1c l\u00ean m\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o n\u00e0y, v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, khi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a CLB, m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea1i gia \u0111\u00ecnh Liverpool. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i&rdquo; &ndash; Alisson Becker h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 \u0110T Brazil \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi 17/37 tr\u1eadn ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i Serie A, v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 cao th\u1ee9 3 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u &ndash; ch\u1ec9 sau Jan Oblak v\u00e0 David De Gea. Anh l\u00e0 m\u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool, khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 Fabinho, Keita v\u00e0 Shaqiri m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-blackburn-02-liverpool-giao-huu-he-2018-326-191631.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/tong-hop-blackburn-02-liverpool-giao-huu-he-2018.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-blackburn-02-liverpool-giao-huu-he-2018-326-191631.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Blackburn 0-2 Liverpool (Giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018)</span><br>\r\nHai pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng trong hi\u1ec7p 2 c\u1ee7a Markovic v\u00e0 Sturridge gi\u00fap L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c th\u1ebf l\u1ef1c m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Premier League nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd \u0111ang ch\u01a1i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t trong...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/mat-alisson-sep-roma-van-day-tu-tin-176-191624.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/mat-alisson-sep-roma-van-day-tu-tin.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/mat-alisson-sep-roma-van-day-tu-tin-176-191624.html\">M\u1ea5t Alisson, s\u1ebfp Roma v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin</span><br>\r\nMonchi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 AS Roma. Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7y tham v\u1ecdng d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t, m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Alisson sang...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1428","checkdouble":"191632"},{"date":"06:20 20/07","title":"Alisson n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/alisson-noi-gi-khi-chinh-thuc-gia-nhap-liverpool.jpeg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Brazil \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Anfield. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi Alisson ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool, sau khi ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 bom t\u1ea5n.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nAlisson ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 chi ti\u1ebft th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao b\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed trong tr\u1eadn Liverpool 5-2 AS Roma &ndash; b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua. S\u1ef1 cu\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a C\u0110V L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf t\u1ea1i Anfield l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn anh \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb trong bu\u1ed5i ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, bom t\u1ea5n 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool cho bi\u1ebft: <em>&ldquo;Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ebfn quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. Khi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0a ra s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 thay \u0111\u1ed5i m\u00e0u \u00e1o, thay \u0111\u1ed5i CLB, m\u00e0 c\u00f2n thay \u0111\u1ed5i to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, gia \u0111\u00ecnh, v\u1ee3 v\u00e0 con g\u00e1i t\u00f4i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</em></div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>&ldquo;Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Liverpool vs Roma r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i c\u0169ng theo d\u00f5i m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1c n\u1eefa. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn phong c\u00e1ch m\u00e0 Jurgen Klopp ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i vui m\u1eebng khi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</em></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>&ldquo;Liverpool l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t CLB kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3, n\u01a1i c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Hy v\u1ecdng, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n l\u1ecbch s\u1eed t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p v\u00e0o qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a CLB.</em><strong><em> Ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y Liverpool l\u1edbn m\u1ea1nh m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa.&rdquo;</em></strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool sau th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Alisson ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool sau th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/ali.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Alisson ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Salah</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Alisson s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean th\u1ee9 2 sau 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Roma, sau ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mohamed Salah. Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp, Alisson cho bi\u1ebft: <em>&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng li\u00ean l\u1ea1c v\u1edbi nhau nhi\u1ec1u k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi anh \u1ea5y r\u1eddi Roma. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 g\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i khi 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 4.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</em></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>&ldquo;H\u00f4m qua, anh \u1ea5y g\u1eedi cho t\u00f4i m\u1ed9t tin nh\u1eafn: &lsquo;N\u00e0y, c\u1eadu c\u00f2n ch\u1edd g\u00ec n\u1eefa&rsquo;. V\u00e0 khi cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111ang trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh, t\u00f4i tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi Salah: &lsquo;B\u00ecnh t\u0129nh n\u00e0o, t\u00f4i \u0111ang \u0111\u1ebfn r\u1ed3i \u0111\u00e2y&rsquo;.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</em></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>&ldquo;T\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 vui m\u1eebng khi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Salah m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, anh \u1ea5y c\u00f2n s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u00e1 t\u00ednh l\u1edbn, nh\u00e2n c\u00e1ch tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi &ndash; \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i&rdquo;</em> &ndash; Alisson ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-liverpool-kich-no-bom-tan-alisson-172-191632.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/chinh-thuc-liverpool-kich-no-bom-tan-alisson.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-liverpool-kich-no-bom-tan-alisson-172-191632.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Liverpool k\u00edch n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n Alisson</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Alisson gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/nhan-vat/alisson-becker-ong-anh-ngo-ngao-va-vinh-quang-den-muon-389-191612.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/alisson-becker-ong-anh-ngo-ngao-va-vinh-quang-den-muon.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/nhan-vat/alisson-becker-ong-anh-ngo-ngao-va-vinh-quang-den-muon-389-191612.html\">Alisson Becker, \u00f4ng anh ng\u1ed5 ng\u00e1o v\u00e0 vinh quang \u0111\u1ebfn mu\u1ed9n</span><br>\r\nL\u00e0 n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a d\u1eady th\u00ec tr\u1ec5, t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n th\u1ea5t th\u1ebf v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f9ng trang l\u1ee9a. Trong b\u00e0i ki\u1ec3m tra d\u1eady th\u00ec, trong khi c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea1t m\u1ee9c n\u0103m (cao...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1427","checkdouble":"191633"},{"date":"06:36 20/07","title":"Klopp chia s\u1ebb nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n bi\u1ebfn Alisson th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/klopp-chia-se-nguyen-nhan-bien-alisson-thanh-thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi.jpeg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i, r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. HLV Jurgen Klopp chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Alisson v\u00e0 t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 m\u1edbi.\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Klopp ch\u1eb3ng ph\u1ea3i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Alisson<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">56 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n ph\u1ee5 ph\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebfn Alisson Becker tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi &ndash; v\u01b0\u1ee3t xa nh\u1eefng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y b\u1eb1ng b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 m\u1ec7nh gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o (Ederson v\u00e0 Buffon). Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi Liverpool, ti\u1ec1n nong kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1, b\u1edfi \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 Jurgen Klopp kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n hay nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn Alisson, HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c cho bi\u1ebft:<em> &ldquo;Trong v\u00e0i tu\u1ea7n qua, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t &ndash; v\u00ec v\u1eady t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i suy ngh\u0129 nhi\u1ec1u. Th\u00fa th\u1ef1c, t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c trao \u0111\u1ed5i nh\u1ecf v\u1edbi BL\u0110. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng, v\u00ec v\u1eady ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</em></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>&ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m. <strong>Ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec v\u1ec1 gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3,</strong> ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng li\u00ean quan t\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, v\u00ec th\u1ebf Liverpool kh\u00f4ng suy ngh\u0129 nhi\u1ec1u. M\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 cho th\u1ea5y t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, t\u1ea1i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y. S\u1ebd c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u chuy\u1ec7n x\u1ea3y ra trong nh\u1eefng tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do Liverpool vui m\u1eebng khi s\u1edf h\u1eefu Alisson ngay b\u00e2y gi\u1edd.&rdquo;</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jurgen Klopp chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Alisson, bom t\u1ea5n 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jurgen Klopp chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Alisson, bom t\u1ea5n 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/klop.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Klopp chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Alisson</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n<em>&ldquo;Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ebfng Anh c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, v\u00e0 Alisson l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u c\u00e1 t\u00ednh. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Roma v\u00e0 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao t\u1ea1i World Cup. \u0110T Brazil \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p may khi d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n Alisson \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t.&rdquo;</em></div>\r\n<div><em> &nbsp;</em></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>&ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1edf h\u1eefu r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m b\u00e2y gi\u1edd l\u00e0 Alisson ph\u1ea3i th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi Premier League. Gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t, tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i, cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng, v\u0103n h\u00f3a, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh. Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng quan tr\u1ecdng, b\u1edfi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Alisson v\u00ec t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</em></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u00e0 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n. Nh\u1eefng n\u0103m t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111ang \u0111\u1ebfn, v\u00ec v\u1eady t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi&rdquo;</em> &ndash; Jurgen Klopp chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Alisson.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/alisson-noi-gi-khi-chinh-thuc-gia-nhap-liverpool-172-191633.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/alisson-noi-gi-khi-chinh-thuc-gia-nhap-liverpool.jpeg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/alisson-noi-gi-khi-chinh-thuc-gia-nhap-liverpool-172-191633.html\">Alisson n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool?</span><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Brazil \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Anfield. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi Alisson ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool, sau khi ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-liverpool-kich-no-bom-tan-alisson-172-191632.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/chinh-thuc-liverpool-kich-no-bom-tan-alisson.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-liverpool-kich-no-bom-tan-alisson-172-191632.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Liverpool k\u00edch n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n Alisson</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Alisson gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/nhan-vat/alisson-becker-ong-anh-ngo-ngao-va-vinh-quang-den-muon-389-191612.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/alisson-becker-ong-anh-ngo-ngao-va-vinh-quang-den-muon.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/nhan-vat/alisson-becker-ong-anh-ngo-ngao-va-vinh-quang-den-muon-389-191612.html\">Alisson Becker, \u00f4ng anh ng\u1ed5 ng\u00e1o v\u00e0 vinh quang \u0111\u1ebfn mu\u1ed9n</span><br>\r\nL\u00e0 n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a d\u1eady th\u00ec tr\u1ec5, t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n th\u1ea5t th\u1ebf v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f9ng trang l\u1ee9a. Trong b\u00e0i ki\u1ec3m tra d\u1eady th\u00ec, trong khi c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea1t m\u1ee9c n\u0103m (cao...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1426","checkdouble":"191634"},{"date":"06:53 20/07","title":"V\u1edbi Alisson, Premier League chi\u1ebfm tr\u1ecdn h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/26/voi-alisson-premier-league-chiem-tron-hang-thu-dat-gia-nhat-hanh-tinh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson Becker v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb h\u01a1n 1 t\u1ef7 b\u1ea3ng.\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c Liverpool c\u0169ng ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Alisson Becker t\u1eeb AS Roma. C\u1ed9ng c\u1ea3 ph\u1ee5 ph\u00ed, t\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf chi ra cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng &ndash; k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n. V\u00e0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafc m\u1eafc r\u1eb1ng Ederson hay Buffon m\u1edbi l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u1eaft nh\u1ea5t (do ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch gi\u1eefa \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 euro).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Premier League c\u0169ng ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 ch\u1ec9 trong 2 n\u0103m (k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb 6/2016). C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Alisson, Liverpool c\u0169ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Virgil Van Dijk &ndash; trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. 3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Man City d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Pep Guardiola &ndash; \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Kyle Walker, John Stones v\u00e0 Benjamin Mendy.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Premier League chi\u1ebfm n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Premier League chi\u1ebfm n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/Premier-League-chiem-nua-doi-hinh-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Alisson gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nTr\u00ean h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7, n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh c\u0169ng g\u00f3p 1 c\u00e1i t\u00ean l\u00e0 Paul Pogba &ndash; \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c M.U chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2016 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. X\u00e9t theo v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3, 2 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p c\u00f9ng Pogba trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 James Rodriguez (71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng) v\u00e0 Philippe Coutinho (142 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng).</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, si\u00eau sao Cristiano Ronaldo l\u0129nh x\u1ee9ng v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 115 tri\u1ec7u euro (99,2 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng) khi gia nh\u1eadp Juventus m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. 2 c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i c\u1ee7a PSG &ndash; &ldquo;k\u1ecbch s\u0129&rdquo; Neymar c\u00f9ng &ldquo;si\u00eau xe&rdquo; Kylian Mbappe.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, t\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 1056 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Premier League c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1edbi danh s\u00e1ch n\u00e0y, khi h\u1ecd chi\u1ebfm 6/11 c\u00e1i t\u00ean trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh (ch\u1ec9 x\u00e9t t\u1eebng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed, kh\u00f4ng t\u00ednh th\u1ee9 t\u1ef1).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/team.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. \u1ea2nh: B/R Football</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-chia-se-nguyen-nhan-bien-alisson-thanh-thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi-172-191634.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/klopp-chia-se-nguyen-nhan-bien-alisson-thanh-thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi.jpeg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-chia-se-nguyen-nhan-bien-alisson-thanh-thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi-172-191634.html\">Klopp chia s\u1ebb nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n bi\u1ebfn Alisson th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</span><br>\r\nSau nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i, r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. HLV Jurgen Klopp chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Alisson v\u00e0 t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u1eadu...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/alisson-noi-gi-khi-chinh-thuc-gia-nhap-liverpool-172-191633.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/alisson-noi-gi-khi-chinh-thuc-gia-nhap-liverpool.jpeg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/alisson-noi-gi-khi-chinh-thuc-gia-nhap-liverpool-172-191633.html\">Alisson n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool?</span><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Brazil \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Anfield. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi Alisson ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool, sau khi ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nNguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1425","checkdouble":"191635"},{"date":"06:58 20/07","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay (20/7/2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/20/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-2072018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay 20/7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u00f4ng tin ng\u00e0y gi\u1edd c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 di\u1ec5n ra h\u00f4m nay v\u00e0 \u0111\u00eam/r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y mai.</h2><div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-bong-da/lich-thi-dau-icc-2018-ket-qua-international-champions-cup-279-190766.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/131008-lich-thi-dau-icc-2018-ket-qua-international-champions-cup.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-bong-da/lich-thi-dau-icc-2018-ket-qua-international-champions-cup-279-190766.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u ICC 2018 - K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 International Champions Cup</span><br>\r\n<span>Bongda24h.vn c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u ICC 2018 v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 International Champions Cup, gi\u1ea3i \u0